uture project plans news & announcements teaching law in afghanistan and other developing nations stanford law school makes legal education a global goal june 28 2010 stanford university news related erik jensen larry kramer afghanistan legal education project bhutan law and policy project rule of law program recorded & past events january 2012 join sls rule of law projects january 26 2012 from 12 45 pm 2 00 pm contact information stanford law school bhutan law and policy project related rule of law program cloudy 45 f 2012 stanford university system requirements help virtual tour
